{"word":"ἐκκόπτω","slug":"ἐκκόπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰϰόπτω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κόπτω\">κόπτω</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκκοπή\">ἐκκοπή</a></el> and <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κοπή\">κοπή</a></el>] ‘eliminate by cutting’, <b>cut out,</b> a tree chop down <b><a href='B:470 3:10'>Mt 3:10</a>,</b> and so in all the gospel <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a>; a branch <b><a href='B:520 11:22'>Ro 11:22</a>, <a href='B:520 11:24'>24</a>;</b> in imagery <b>cut off, do away with</b> a pretext <b><a href='B:540 11:12'>2 Cor 11:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκκοπήσῃ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκκρεμάννυμι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}